<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
<title>D-Reflection Note | 大東文化大学</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --gd:#1E3A0F; --gm:#3B6621; --gl:#568C30; --ga:#7DB54C;
  --gp:#C8E4A0; --gbg:#EBF4DF; --white:#fff;
  --txt:#1A2A0F; --muted:#5A6E50; --border:#B8D898;
  --s1:#C62828;--s2:#E65100;--s3:#D4A017;--s4:#3D7A2B;--s5:#1B5E20;
  --r:14px; --sh:0 2px 16px rgba(30,58,15,.10);
}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
html,body{height:100%;overflow:hidden;}
#app{
  font-family:'Noto Sans JP',-apple-system,sans-serif;
  background:var(--gbg);color:var(--txt);
  max-width:500px;margin:0 auto;height:100dvh;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;
}
.sc{display:none;flex:1;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden;}
.sc.on{display:flex;}
.sa{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:16px;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;}
/* HEADER */
.hdr{background:var(--gd);color:#fff;padding:13px 18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;flex-shrink:0;}
.hdr-logo{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--ga);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;font-size:12px;color:var(--gd);letter-spacing:-1px;flex-shrink:0;}
.hdr h1{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;}.hdr .sub{font-size:10px;opacity:.7;font-weight:400;}
.back-btn{background:none;border:none;color:#fff;font-size:24px;cursor:pointer;padding:2px 6px 2px 0;line-height:1;}
/* BOTTOM NAV */
.bnav{background:var(--white);border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-shrink:0;}
.ni{flex:1;padding:9px 2px 8px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;color:var(--muted);font-family:inherit;}
.ni.on{color:var(--gm);}
.ni-ic{font-size:19px;line-height:1;}.ni-lb{font-size:9.5px;font-weight:500;}
/* INPUTS */
.inp{width:100%;padding:12px 14px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;font-family:inherit;font-size:15px;color:var(--txt);background:#fff;-webkit-appearance:none;}
.inp:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--gm);}
.ta{width:100%;padding:12px 14px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;font-family:inherit;font-size:14px;color:var(--txt);resize:vertical;min-height:80px;line-height:1.7;-webkit-appearance:none;}
.ta:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--gm);}
.fg{margin-bottom:14px;}
.fl{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--txt);margin-bottom:6px;display:block;}
.fl .req{color:var(--s1);margin-left:3px;}
.fl .hint{font-size:11px;font-weight:400;color:var(--muted);margin-left:6px;}
/* BUTTONS */
.btn{width:100%;padding:14px;background:var(--gm);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:12px;font-family:inherit;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:.02em;transition:opacity .15s,transform .1s;}
.btn:active{transform:scale(.98);opacity:.9;}
.btn2{width:100%;padding:12px;background:var(--gbg);color:var(--gm);border:1.5px solid var(--ga);border-radius:12px;font-family:inherit;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;}
.btn-sm{padding:8px 14px;background:var(--gbg);color:var(--gm);border:1.5px solid var(--ga);border-radius:8px;font-family:inherit;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;}
/* CARDS */
.card{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r);padding:16px;margin-bottom:12px;box-shadow:var(--sh);}
.ctit{font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.07em;margin-bottom:12px;}
/* SCALE */
.sc-wrap{margin-bottom:16px;}
.sc-lbl{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:7px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}
.sc-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:400;}
.sc-row{display:flex;gap:6px;}
.sb{flex:1;padding:11px 4px;border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;font-family:inherit;font-size:18px;font-weight:900;cursor:pointer;background:#fff;color:var(--muted);transition:all .12s;}
.sb.s1{background:#FFEBEE;border-color:var(--s1);color:var(--s1);}
.sb.s2{background:#FFF3E0;border-color:var(--s2);color:var(--s2);}
.sb.s3{background:#FFFDE7;border-color:var(--s3);color:var(--s3);}
.sb.s4{background:#F1F8E9;border-color:var(--s4);color:var(--s4);}
.sb.s5{background:#E8F5E9;border-color:var(--s5);color:var(--s5);}
.sc-hints{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:3px;}.sc-hint{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);}
/* INJURY */
.inj-row{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:10px;}
.tb{flex:1;padding:10px;border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;font-family:inherit;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;background:#fff;color:var(--muted);}
.tb.no{background:#E8F5E9;border-color:var(--s5);color:var(--s5);}.tb.yes{background:#FFEBEE;border-color:var(--s1);color:var(--s1);}
/* HISTORY ITEMS */
.ei{background:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:13px 15px;margin-bottom:8px;box-shadow:var(--sh);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:transform .1s;}
.ei:active{transform:scale(.98);}
.edb{text-align:center;min-width:46px;background:var(--gbg);border-radius:10px;padding:8px 6px;}
.ed{font-size:22px;font-weight:900;color:var(--gm);line-height:1;}.em{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500;}
.ei-info{flex:1;}.ei-t{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:3px;}.ei-m{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);}
.scbadge{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;font-weight:900;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
/* WEEKLY */
.wsel{background:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:12px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:14px;box-shadow:var(--sh);}
.wnb{background:var(--gbg);border:none;border-radius:8px;width:36px;height:36px;font-size:18px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.wlbl{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;}.wdt{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);}
/* VIEW */
.dr{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gbg);}
.dr:last-child{border-bottom:none;}.dk{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);}.dv{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;text-align:right;max-width:62%;}
/* MISC */
.notice{background:var(--gbg);border-left:4px solid var(--ga);border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:10px 14px;font-size:12px;color:var(--gm);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:14px;}
.stit{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);margin:12px 0 6px;}
.empty{text-align:center;padding:40px 20px;color:var(--muted);}
.empty-ic{font-size:48px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.tw{display:flex;gap:12px;}.tc{flex:1;}
.wr{position:relative;}.wu{position:absolute;right:14px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:700;}
.sbw{padding:14px 0 6px;}
#toast{position:fixed;bottom:80px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(12px);background:var(--s5);color:#fff;padding:10px 24px;border-radius:24px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;opacity:0;transition:all .25s;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;white-space:nowrap;}
#toast.show{opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0);}

/* ===== INTRO SCREEN ===== */
#si .intro-top{background:linear-gradient(155deg,var(--gd) 0%,var(--gm) 100%);padding:36px 24px 28px;color:#fff;text-align:center;}
#si .intro-logo{width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:16px;background:var(--ga);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;font-size:18px;color:var(--gd);margin:0 auto 14px;letter-spacing:-2px;}
#si .intro-title{font-size:24px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.02em;margin-bottom:4px;}
#si .intro-sub{font-size:11px;opacity:.8;line-height:1.6;}
.intro-body{padding:20px 20px 0;}
.intro-section-label{font-size:13px;font-weight:900;color:var(--gm);border-left:4px solid var(--ga);padding-left:10px;margin-bottom:10px;}
.intro-text{font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.95;color:var(--txt);margin-bottom:16px;}
.intro-quote{background:var(--gd);color:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:18px 20px;margin-bottom:16px;position:relative;}
.intro-quote-text{font-size:14px;line-height:1.9;font-weight:500;}
.intro-quote-kagi{font-size:18px;font-weight:900;color:var(--ga);line-height:1;vertical-align:-.05em;}
.intro-attr{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-align:right;margin-bottom:20px;line-height:1.7;}
.intro-notice{background:var(--gbg);border:1.5px solid var(--gp);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:20px;}
.intro-notice strong{color:var(--gm);}

/* ===== WELCOME (PROFILE SETUP) ===== */
#sw .profile-top{background:var(--gd);color:#fff;padding:14px 20px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
#sw .profile-top .logo{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--ga);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;font-size:12px;color:var(--gd);letter-spacing:-1px;flex-shrink:0;}
#sw .profile-top h1{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;}.sw-sub{font-size:10px;opacity:.7;}
.profile-section{margin-bottom:8px;}
.profile-section-hdr{font-size:12px;font-weight:900;color:var(--white);background:var(--gm);padding:8px 14px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:10px;letter-spacing:.04em;}

/* ===== HOME ===== */
.home-top{background:linear-gradient(145deg,var(--gd) 0%,var(--gm) 100%);padding:20px 20px 30px;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
.gt{font-size:12px;opacity:.8;margin-bottom:3px;}.gn{font-size:22px;font-weight:900;}
.sbadge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;margin-top:10px;}
.today-card{margin:-14px 14px 0;background:#fff;border-radius:var(--r);padding:14px 16px;box-shadow:var(--sh);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0;}
.st-dot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;}.st-dot.ok{background:var(--s5);}.st-dot.ng{background:var(--s2);}
.st-txt{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;}.st-dt{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);}
/* Goals card */
.goal-card{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r);padding:16px;margin-bottom:12px;box-shadow:var(--sh);border-left:4px solid var(--gm);}
.goal-card-hdr{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:12px;}
.goal-card-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:900;color:var(--gm);}
.goal-item{margin-bottom:10px;padding-bottom:10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gbg);}
.goal-item:last-child{margin-bottom:0;padding-bottom:0;border-bottom:none;}
.goal-item-label{font-size:10.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:4px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;}
.goal-item-text{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--txt);line-height:1.6;}
.goal-item-text.motto{font-size:15px;color:var(--gm);font-style:italic;}
.goal-empty{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);font-style:italic;}
/* About card on home */
.about-card{background:var(--gd);border-radius:var(--r);padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:12px;cursor:pointer;}
.about-card-inner{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
.about-icon{font-size:24px;flex-shrink:0;}
.about-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;}
.about-sub{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);margin-top:2px;}

/* ===== PDF OVERLAY ===== */
#pdf-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:#f5f5f5;z-index:10000;flex-direction:column;max-width:500px;margin:0 auto;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',-apple-system,sans-serif;}
#pdf-overlay.on{display:flex;}
#pdf-toolbar{background:var(--gd);color:#fff;padding:13px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0;}
#pdf-toolbar .tl{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;}.#pdf-toolbar .ts{font-size:10px;opacity:.7;margin-top:2px;}
#pdf-content{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:12px;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;}
.pdf-actions{background:var(--gd);padding:14px 16px;display:flex;gap:10px;flex-shrink:0;}
.btn-print{flex:2;padding:14px;background:var(--ga);color:var(--gd);border:none;border-radius:12px;font-family:inherit;font-size:15px;font-weight:900;cursor:pointer;}
.btn-cpdf{flex:1;padding:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:12px;font-family:inherit;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;}

/* ===== REPORT STYLES ===== */
.rpt{background:#fff;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11pt;color:#1A2A0F;}
.rpt-hdr{background:#1E3A0F;color:#fff;padding:12px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
.rpt-hdr-logo{font-size:22pt;font-weight:900;color:#7DB54C;letter-spacing:-2px;}
.rpt-hdr-title{font-size:15pt;font-weight:900;}.rpt-hdr-sub{font-size:9pt;opacity:.8;margin-top:2px;}
.rpt-info{background:#EBF4DF;padding:8px 16px;border-bottom:2px solid #3B6621;}
.rpt-info table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:10pt;}
.rpt-info td{padding:3px 6px 3px 0;}.rpt-info .lbl{color:#5A6E50;font-weight:700;white-space:nowrap;}.rpt-info .val{color:#1A2A0F;font-weight:900;}
.rpt-goals{border:1px solid #B8D898;border-radius:6px;margin:10px 16px;overflow:hidden;}
.rpt-goals-hdr{background:#568C30;color:#fff;padding:6px 12px;font-size:10pt;font-weight:700;}
.rpt-goals-body{padding:8px 12px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;}
.rpt-goal-item .rgl{font-size:8.5pt;color:#5A6E50;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:2px;}
.rpt-goal-item .rgv{font-size:10pt;line-height:1.6;}
.rpt-motto{grid-column:1/-1;}
.rpt-sec{padding:10px 16px 0;}
.rpt-sec-tit{font-size:11pt;font-weight:900;color:#1E3A0F;border-bottom:2px solid #3B6621;padding-bottom:4px;margin-bottom:10px;}
.rpt-tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:9pt;margin-bottom:14px;}
.rpt-tbl th{background:#3B6621;color:#fff;padding:5px 4px;text-align:center;font-weight:700;font-size:8.5pt;}
.rpt-tbl td{padding:4px 4px;border:1px solid #C8E4A0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;}
.rpt-tbl tr:nth-child(even) td{background:#F5FAF0;}
.rpt-tbl .tl{text-align:left;}.rpt-tbl .sm{font-size:8pt;}
.rpt-dot{display:inline-block;width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;color:#fff;font-size:9pt;font-weight:900;line-height:18px;text-align:center;}
.rpt-week{margin-bottom:10px;border:1px solid #B8D898;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;}
.rpt-week-hdr{background:#568C30;color:#fff;padding:6px 12px;font-size:10pt;font-weight:700;}
.rpt-week-body{padding:10px 12px;}
.rpt-wlbl{font-size:9pt;font-weight:700;color:#5A6E50;margin-bottom:3px;margin-top:6px;}.rpt-wlbl:first-child{margin-top:0;}
.rpt-wval{font-size:10pt;line-height:1.7;white-space:pre-wrap;margin-bottom:4px;}
.rpt-note{margin-bottom:8px;border-left:3px solid #7DB54C;padding:7px 12px;background:#F5FAF0;}
.rpt-note-dt{font-size:9.5pt;font-weight:700;color:#3B6621;margin-bottom:3px;}
.rpt-note-lbl{font-size:8.5pt;color:#5A6E50;font-weight:700;margin-top:4px;margin-bottom:2px;}
.rpt-note-val{font-size:9.5pt;line-height:1.6;white-space:pre-wrap;}
.rpt-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.rpt-stat{background:#EBF4DF;border-radius:8px;padding:8px;text-align:center;}
.rpt-stat-lbl{font-size:8.5pt;color:#5A6E50;margin-bottom:2px;}.rpt-stat-val{font-size:15pt;font-weight:900;color:#3B6621;line-height:1.1;}.rpt-stat-sub{font-size:8pt;color:#5A6E50;}
.rpt-footer{border-top:1px solid #C8E4A0;padding:12px 16px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;margin-top:10px;}
.rpt-sig{border-bottom:1px solid #1A2A0F;width:100px;text-align:center;padding-bottom:2px;font-size:9pt;}

@media print{
  html,body{overflow:visible!important;height:auto!important;max-width:100%!important;}
  #app{display:none!important;}
  #pdf-overlay{
    display:block!important;position:static!important;
    max-width:100%!important;width:100%!important;
    height:auto!important;overflow:visible!important;
    background:#fff!important;z-index:auto!important;
    inset:auto!important;
  }
  #pdf-toolbar,.pdf-actions{display:none!important;}
  #pdf-content{
    overflow:visible!important;height:auto!important;
    padding:0!important;background:#fff!important;
  }
  .rpt{font-size:10pt;}
  @page{size:A4 portrait;margin:10mm 12mm;}
  .rpt-sec{padding:10px 0 0;}
  .rpt-goals{margin:10px 0;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="toast">✓ 保存しました</div>

<div id="app">

<!-- ===== INTRO (D-reflection Note とは) ===== -->
<div class="sc on" id="si">
  <div class="intro-top">
    <div class="intro-logo">DR</div>
    <div class="intro-title">D-Reflection Note</div>
    <div class="intro-sub">大東文化大学 スポーツ・健康科学部<br>スポーツフィールドワーク</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sa">
    <div class="intro-body">
      <div class="intro-section-label">D-reflection Note とは</div>
      <div class="intro-text">
        D-reflection Note はトレーニング目標を設定し、目標達成のための行動記録を記し、課題を言語化することで、自らの行動を客観的に見つめなおすためのノートである。
      </div>
      <div class="intro-text">
        人間の脳は都合の良いことを記憶し、苦痛になることを忘れやすい特性がある。スポーツは目標を達成するにあたり、失敗の連続であり、失敗に対してあきらめずに、しかも合理的、効率的な方法を選択し、取り組み続けなければならない。<br><br>
        すなわち、アスリートとして目標を達成するためには、日々の課題を視覚化（明確化）し自らの欠点と向き合う<strong>レジリエンス（粘り強さ）</strong>が求められる。<br>
        この日誌の作成を通して、成功への一助としてもらいたい。
      </div>
      <div class="intro-quote">
        <div class="intro-quote-text"><span class="intro-quote-kagi">『</span>最も努力した選手が成功するとは限らない。それでも、諦めなかったものだけが成功に到達する。<span class="intro-quote-kagi">』</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-attr">大東文化大学<br>スポーツフィールドワーク担当教員</div>
      <div class="intro-notice">
        <strong>📱 このアプリについて</strong><br>
        スマートフォンで毎日の練習記録、体調、疲労感などを入力できます。月末にPDFに変換して提出してください。<br><br>
        <strong>📌 月間目標・週間目標は紙に書いて掲示しましょう</strong>
      </div>
      <div style="padding-bottom:16px;">
        <button class="btn" onclick="goToProfile()">プロフィールを設定してはじめる →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== PROFILE SETUP ===== -->
<div class="sc" id="sw">
  <div class="profile-top">
    <div class="logo">DR</div>
    <div><div class="sw-sub">D-Reflection Note</div><h1>プロフィール設定</h1></div>
  </div>
  <div class="sa">
    <div class="profile-section">
      <div class="profile-section-hdr">👤 基本情報</div>
      <div class="fg"><label class="fl">氏名<span class="req">*</span></label><input id="inp-name" class="inp" type="text" placeholder="例：田中 太郎"></div>
      <div class="fg"><label class="fl">学籍番号</label><input id="inp-sid" class="inp" type="text" placeholder="例：A2300001"></div>
      <div class="fg"><label class="fl">担当スポーツ・種目</label><input id="inp-sport" class="inp" type="text" placeholder="例：サッカー、バスケットボール"></div>
